data.description: Welcome to your new home! This beautiful single-story house has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and is perfectly situated on a corner lot with no HOA and a brand new RV Gate! Inside, the home features an inviting open concept that seamlessly connects the kitchen, living room, and dining area. The layout creates a spacious and welcoming atmosphere for both everyday living and entertaining. This home is brimming with ''NEW''. NEW flooring, carpet, interior paint, bathroom vanities, toilets, kitchen appliances, kitchen ceiling fans, and door to the backyard! Additionally, a brand new cement wall has just been completed, providing security and privacy, while the new RV gate offers convenience for those with larger vehicles. This home is an incredible opportunity that you won't want to miss.
